%% title: fig-01 maturity model
%% chapter: CH01
%% caption: Prompt / Context / Harness stack in the order that reduces wrong answers, forgetting, and breaking things or stopping early.
flowchart LR
    P[Prompt Engineering<br/>Fix what the agent is asked to do] --> C[Context Engineering<br/>Fix what the agent keeps seeing]
    C --> H[Harness Engineering<br/>Fix how execution and verification close]
    P -.-> P1[Reduce wrong answers]
    C -.-> C1[Reduce forgetting]
    H -.-> H1[Reduce breakage and early stops]
